@@ -640,0 +640,10 @@ + *

+ * The implementation of this method is equivalent to: + * {@snippet lang="java" : + * return (int) getBytesRead(); + * } + *

+ * If the number of compressed bytes is greater than {@link Integer#MAX_VALUE}, + * the narrowing conversion to int causes the highest 32 bits of + * the number to be discarded. The value returned in such cases will be incorrect + * and may even be a negative number.
